Package: HMLCDM
Title: Variational Inference Algorithm for Hidden Markov Longitudinal Cognitive Diagnostic Models
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: 
    person("Hao", "Duan", , "hduan7@ucla.edu", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Implements a variational inference algorithm for Hidden Markov 
    Longitudinal Cognitive Diagnostic Models using R with a torch backend. 
    This package provides tools for fitting and analyzing cognitive diagnostic 
    models with longitudinal data structures.
